::Rex/DevilDuer::

Rex stops in his tracks as he his wrist comp alerts him of someone knocking 
on the door (its actually a hatch-type of thing) of the Cybertronian Fire. He 
retraces his steps, walking up to the door.

He pushes a button, the door opening. Rex looks Sinister over. "Are you a 
Maximal?" he asks, gun ready just in case.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DevilDuer turns around as his room's comp beeps, seeing a new pod fall. He 
jumps up. At least it was something to take his mind off of Feline!

"Hey, Zardus, there's a new pod in the middle of nowhere, want me to pick it 
up?" DevilDuer asks into his comm-link.

"Go ahead," Zardus' voice responds, DevilDuer exiting his quarters.
